{"id":2309,"date":"2024-11-28T20:05:15","date_gmt":"2024-11-28T20:05:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2309"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:15:54","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:15:54","slug":"happiness-increaser","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/happiness-increaser\/","title":{"rendered":"Happiness Increaser (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Dehara City<\/strong> &#8211; Inside of the house directly south of the Rift Cave entrance.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Plays with the selected Pokemon in the player\u2019s party to increase its overall happiness.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>N\/A<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>Free<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Dehara City Pokemon Center and follow the path north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-walking-north-from-the-dehara-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Walking north from the Dehara City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking north from the Dehara City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk past the first house to your east and enter the second one.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-south-of-rift-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house south of Rift Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house south of Rift Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside the house, interact with the closed doors to open them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-interacting-with-the-closed-doors.jpg\" alt=\"Interacting with the closed doors. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Interacting with the closed doors.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Happiness Increaser is the little boy inside the room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-happiness-increaser.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Happiness Increaser. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Happiness Increaser.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-happiness-increaser-asking-to-play-with-a-pokemon.jpg\" alt=\"The Happiness Increaser asking to play with a Pokemon. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Happiness Increaser asking to play with a Pokemon.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Happiness Increaser plays with any selected Pokemon to increase its overall happiness for free. However, this event can only happen once per day.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2310,"parent":2143,"menu_